In this episode of So This Happened, we review the threat issued by the Central Bank of Nigeria to Nigerians who are fond of mutilating, defacing, squeezing, and even spraying the naira notes. Talk of a low tolerance level, Lagos Businesswoman Alhaja Adeleke, arrested for pouring hot water on sales girl and locking her up. Lastly, we reviewed the famous Denmark footballer, Christian Eriksen, who suffered a cardiac arrest during the Euro 2020 clash with Finland.